<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="while-n">while <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /waɪl/    美 /waɪl/  </p>
<p>[U] </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>一段时间；一会儿：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>once in a while</strong>
偶尔；间或</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Would you like to come in and rest <strong>for a while</strong>?
你要不要进来休息一会儿？</p><footer>译林③ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The file may <strong>take a short while</strong> to download.
下载这个文件可能需要点儿时间。</p></div></div>